About
-----
Rhythmbox Skype Mood Notifier - is a rhythmbox plugin that updates 
Skype mood text (in artist - album - title format) from current playing song/music 

Features
--------
v0.40
- fix longest running bug #0001 ItsBlueB
- tested against ubuntu netbook 10.10
- overhaul'ed SkypeRhythmboxMediator (spaghetti call)
- added experimental radio station NOTE: you can change __init__.py line 160
    if (station is not None) : formatted_mood = "%s :: %s" % (station,formatted_mood)
  this will concatenate a some characters before the skype mood " [station-name] :: "


v0.35
- fix plugin version display
- added credits
- tested @ new ubuntu 10.04 LTS x86-64
- added $ALBUM support (thanks to eremit's patch)

v0.30
- moved config file to gconf

v0.25
- added a configuration dialog box for custom mood message

v0.2
- pause / resume Rhythmbox if there is a call

v0.01
- updates mood from local playing music
- updates mood from streaming / shoutcast

